\c 52 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 52\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Wanta Dhuma Irratti Nama Dira'aa Eeggatu (Geggeessituu warra faarfatootaaf; kun mararoo Daawit isa yeroo Do'eeg namichi Edoom dhufee, "Daawit gara mana Ahiimelek dhufeera" jedhee Saa'olitti hime faarfatamee dha)
\m \bd 1\bd* Gaarummaan Waaqayyoo guyyaa hundumaa achuma jira; ati immoo yaa nama dira'aa, hamaa hojjechuu keetiin maaliif of jajja ree?
\m \bd 2\bd* Yaa isa haxxummaadhaan hojjettuu, itti yaaddee wanta badiisaa in qopheessita; arrabni kee akka qarabaa qaramaa dha.
\m \bd 3\bd* Ati wanta gaarii caalaa wanta hamaa, dhugaa dubbachuu caalaas soba in jaallatta.
\m \bd 4\bd* Yaa arraba haxxummaa dubbattuu, ati dubbii badiisaa in jaallatta.
\m \bd 5\bd* Waaqayyo garuu yeroo hundumaaf gad si cabsuuf jira; godoo kee keessaa butee si baasuuf jira; biyya warra jiraatoo keessaas hundeedhaan si buqqisa. 
\m \bd 6\bd* Warri qajeelonni kana arganii in sodaatu, namichatti garuu kolfaa in dubbatu, \bd 7\bd* "Ilaa namicha isa Waaqayyoon da'oo isaa hin godhanne, qooda kanaa baay'ina sooruma isaa amanatee, badiisa fiduu isaatiinis jabaa of se'e" in jedhu.
\m \bd 8\bd* Ani garuu akka muka ejersaa, isa mana Waaqayyoo keessatti lalisaa guddatuu ti; yeroo hundumaas bara baraan gaarummaa Waaqayyoo nan amanadha.
\m \bd 9\bd* Ati kana waan gooteef, ani yeroo hundumaa galateeffachaa sin jajadha; namoota siif of kennan durattis, maqaa kee isa gaarii abdiidhaan nan waammadha.
\b 
